                "description": {
                    "value": "<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature approaches within 5 feet of the hatchet or more than 3 creatures enter area C10;</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The furious shriek of Asethanna's rage resonates throughout the room, and all creatures within 25 feet of the hatchet must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-traits=\"auditory,emotion,fear,mental,occult\" data-pf2-label=\"Furious Shriek DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"25\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save. The haunt then rolls initiative.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature feels as if the wrathful haunt is particularly enraged at them. The creature becomes frightened 2; their frightened condition doesn't decrease automatically as long as the haunt remains active, and the hatchet gains a +2 circumstance bonus to all wrathful hatchet Strikes it attempts against the creature.</p>\n</div>"
